The '''Interstellar Survey Corps''' were the predecessors of the [[Imperial Survey Corps/Legends|Imperial Survey Corps]], and worked for the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. One of their four man ships landed on an unknown jungle planet which contained the [[Dark Side pyramids]], though all crewmembers were killed by the [[Dark Side wraith]]s and their spirits were trapped in the [[Altar of the Dark Side]]. It was from these members that [[Master]] [[Zik'tath]] learned to understand and speak [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]].

